	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('IDogaHRtbGVudGl0aWVzKCRlLT5nZXRNZXNzYWdlKCkpOwoJZWNobyAkaHRtbG1zZzsKfQo='));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('cron.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: cron.php');
	writefile_4();
	if (!is_file('cron.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): cron.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('cron.php') != 'c6b2d8260670553348f9bc1e3d7bb53a881b2f00') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): cron.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('cron.php', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of cron.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('cron.php') !== 'c6b2d8260670553348f9bc1e3d7bb53a881b2f00') {
		if (@sha1_file('cron.php') !== 'edfa46a0b24ee1602c3d92f9870382c9f8580302') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: cron.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('cron.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('cron.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('cron.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_4();
		if (@sha1_file('cron.php') !== 'c6b2d8260670553348f9bc1e3d7bb53a881b2f00') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): cron.php');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_18();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_dos.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_dos.php') != 'e8650bef1c107781bc9a809aa17ef1a28b4aeb4a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_dos.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_dos.php', 0644)) {

	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_dos.php') !== 'e8650bef1c107781bc9a809aa17ef1a28b4aeb4a') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_dos.php') !== '61e543b00830d9c732f0c26060f519d1d03f8db1') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_dos.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_dos.php');

			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_dos.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_18();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_dos.php') !== 'e8650bef1c107781bc9a809aa17ef1a28b4aeb4a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_dos.php');

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_win.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_win.php');
	writefile_19();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_win.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_win.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_win.php') != '4ec0cfa4a083301df2ac4e803e8b3d3d8ef8142d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_win.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_win.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_win.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_win.php') !== '4ec0cfa4a083301df2ac4e803e8b3d3d8ef8142d') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_win.php') !== '0b7934ce0795a6984a4bf9aaa36394c01f9edb65') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_win.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_win.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_win.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_win.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_19();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_win.php') !== '4ec0cfa4a083301df2ac4e803e8b3d3d8ef8142d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/920_nostalgia/export_win.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	writefile_20();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') != 'a4d435768505ecc4a0b25b96b6d36e10655dd08c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== 'a4d435768505ecc4a0b25b96b6d36e10655dd08c') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '5c613f2685d8ad7c9dd41debb050b4db95c0163e') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_20();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== 'a4d435768505ecc4a0b25b96b6d36e10655dd08c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_24();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php') != 'f3518b00995d4f643d344ca4fe6e0557cf00a9fa') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php') !== 'f3518b00995d4f643d344ca4fe6e0557cf00a9fa') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php') !== 'b67aaa028398643a494279f3877fd5ce7ce572b5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_24();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php') !== 'f3518b00995d4f643d344ca4fe6e0557cf00a9fa') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/095_attachments/download.php');
		}

}

				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_28();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/raPages/910_automated_ajax_calls/OIDplusPageRaAutomatedAJAXCalls.class.php') !== '26cb1e714d7b58fdf5e5700a901fc371ff0b9d98') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/raPages/910_automated_ajax_calls/OIDplusPageRaAutomatedAJAXCalls.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: systeminfo.php');
	writefile_29();
	if (!is_file('systeminfo.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): systeminfo.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('systeminfo.php') != '85ecbf0b3631a56106f669d606b53cdbd8fc250b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): systeminfo.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('systeminfo.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of systeminfo.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('systeminfo.php') !== '85ecbf0b3631a56106f669d606b53cdbd8fc250b') {
		if (@sha1_file('systeminfo.php') !== '953487652288228f29f1ce01f8df0159edf0a40a') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: systeminfo.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('systeminfo.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('systeminfo.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('systeminfo.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_29();
		if (@sha1_file('systeminfo.php') !== '85ecbf0b3631a56106f669d606b53cdbd8fc250b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): systeminfo.php');
		}
	}
}
